Real Estate Market Trends Dashboard
Overview

The Real Estate Market Trends Dashboard is an interactive Power BI project developed as part of my internship. The dashboard provides comprehensive insights into the real estate market by analyzing property prices, rental yields, market demand, supply conditions, and key economic indicators. It helps investors, developers, and business analysts make informed investment and development decisions.

Objective

The objective of this project is to analyze real estate market dynamics using interactive visualizations and geographical analysis to identify profitable investment opportunities and market trends.

Key Features

Property Price Analysis
Analyze average property prices across different locations.
Compare residential and commercial property prices.
Monitor price trends over time.

Rental Yield Analysis
Calculate and compare rental yields.
Identify areas with the highest return on investment (ROI).
Analyze rental income patterns.

Market Demand & Supply
Track property demand and supply.
Identify high-demand and low-supply markets.
Monitor market growth and availability.

Economic Indicators
Analyze the impact of economic factors on property prices.
Compare market performance with economic trends.
Support investment planning using data-driven insights.

Geographical Analysis
Interactive heat maps to identify market hotspots.
Location-based comparison of property values.
Regional investment opportunity analysis.

Dashboard Insights

Property price distribution by location.
Rental yield comparison across cities or regions.
Demand and supply analysis.
Market hotspot identification using heat maps.
Investment opportunity analysis.
Economic trend visualization.

